reviewText: Item received very quickly and was as advertised.

This is first video of the six videos in the Candid Candid Camera series. I had hoped the complete set of six videos would come out on DVD, but so far haven't. This video had topless and completely nude female models in various Candid Camera setups like a topless window washer,  a setup where a door fell over, and a model behind a mirror that was transparent or not depending on the lighting.
